properties.Name: AssetStatusType
properties.Description:
A status type that may be applied to an asset for a period of time.

Ex:
- Operational
- In Maintenance
- In Repair
- Out Of Operation
- In Consignment
- In Storage
- Retired
- In Salvage
- Abandoned
- Unknown

where:

OPERATIONAL
The asset is in operation.

IN MAINTENANCE
The asset is in maintenance.

IN REPAIR
The asset is in repair.

IN CONSIGNMENT
The asset is under consignment.

IN STORAGE
The asset is in-storage

RETIRED
The asset has been retired from service.

IN SALVAGE
Taking components from a piece of (usually outdated or non-functional) property for use in one or more other pieces of property
